<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你现在知道为什么国王喜欢阿拉丁的故事了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为它太刺激了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到现在，你可能已经知道马格里布是一个邪恶的魔法师了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他根本就不是阿拉丁的伯父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布对阿拉丁和他妈妈说了许多谎话！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么？我告诉你吧，他想得到那盏灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布并不是出生于阿拉丁生活的城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是在埃及开罗长大的一个怪孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的双眼苍白而不友善。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>头发是铁锈的颜色，零乱地向四周散开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别人对他笑的时候，他从来不对别人笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从来不像其他孩子一样出去玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他独自待在房间里，读那些满是灰尘的破旧的魔法书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布学会了说咒语，从星象中推测未来，还有制作毒药！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当马格里布长大一些的时候，他去拜访了开罗的大魔法师们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把所有的法术和秘密都教给了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻的马格里布很快就超越了他的老师，但是他仍然继续学习了四十年的魔法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得他已经知道了一切，但是一天深夜，他拥有了一个重大的发现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布读了一本关于国王的宝库的古老书籍，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>书中讲述了一个装满黄金和珠宝的魔法宝库！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而那个宝库里最好的宝物则是一盏朴素的铜灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以在脑海中想象老马格里布在他阴暗的图书馆里的样子吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在书堆里面走来走去，无法停止思考那盏灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他非常渴望得到它！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是有一个问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个世界上只有一个人可以进入宝库。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有一个人能找到那盏灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人便是一个穷裁缝的儿子，名叫阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而这个孩子就住在宝库所在的城市里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么是这个男孩儿？”马格里布不太明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那本古老的书解释了宝库里面的各种骗术和陷阱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是它并没有说明为什么只有阿拉丁可以拿到那盏灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须要找到那个男孩儿！”马格里布说，“那么灯就是我的了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是马格里布航行在大海的边缘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他加入了一个骆驼队，来到了阿拉丁所在的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始在每个地方寻找那个男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们知道，他最终成功找到了阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>经过这么多年和漫长的旅程，成功就在马格里布眼前了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以想象一下当阿拉丁不给马格里布灯时，他的心情会是怎样！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的贪心让他不能再等下去了，所以他变得非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他失去了控制，关上宝库的门，把阿拉丁埋在下面了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布因为生气得到了什么好处吗？没错，他惩罚了阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是马格里布还是没有拿到那盏灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那盏灯和小男孩一起，被紧紧地关在了底下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布接下来会做什么呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打包了自己的行李，离开了这座城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他回到了埃及，独自坐着，脑子里充满了黑暗、不幸的想法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那么阿拉丁做了什么呢？很快你们就会知道了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>